<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Meu perfil - Busca+</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/profile.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/auth.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="profile-shell">
    <header class="profile-topbar">
      <a href="/" class="profile-logo">Busca<span>+</span></a>
      <div class="profile-topbar-actions">
        <button type="button" class="nav-auth-btn" data-auth-open="login">Login</button>
        <a href="/profile" class="nav-profile-link" data-auth-profile-link="true" hidden>
          <img src="" alt="Foto de perfil" class="nav-profile-avatar" data-auth-avatar="true">
          <span data-auth-name="true">Meu perfil</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="profile-layout">
      <section class="profile-hero">
        <span class="profile-kicker">Conta Busca+</span>
        <h1>Seu perfil de busca personalizada</h1>
        <p>Edite seus dados, escolha uma foto e prepare sua conta para alertas, buscas mais inteligentes e futuras assinaturas com monitoramento regional.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="profile-card" data-profile-authenticated="true" hidden>
        <div class="profile-card-header">
          <div class="profile-avatar-block">
            <img src="" alt="Foto de perfil" class="profile-avatar-large" data-profile-avatar-preview="true">
            <div>
              <strong data-profile-display-name="true">Seu nome</strong>
              <span data-profile-display-email="true">email@exemplo.com</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <label class="profile-upload">
            <span class="material-icons">photo_camera</span>
            Alterar foto
            <input type="file" accept="image/*" data-profile-photo-input="true" hidden>
          </label>
        </div>

        <form class="profile-form" data-profile-form="true">
          <label>
            <span>Nome completo</span>
            <input type="text" name="name" required>
          </label>
          <label>
            <span>E-mail</span>
            <input type="email" name="email" required>
          </label>
          <label>
            <span>Telefone</span>
            <input type="text" name="phone" placeholder="(69) 99999-9999">
          </label>
          <label>
            <span>Região de interesse</span>
            <input type="text" name="region" placeholder="Ex.: Cujubim, Rondônia ou região Norte">
          </label>
          <label>
            <span>Temas que acompanha</span>
            <textarea name="interests" rows="4" placeholder="Licitações, saúde, educação, menções ao meu nome..."></textarea>
          </label>

          <div class="profile-switches">
            <label class="profile-switch">
              <input type="checkbox" name="smartSearch">
              <span>Ativar experiência mais personalizada</span>
            </label>
            <label class="profile-switch">
              <input type="checkbox" name="futureAlerts">
              <span>Quero receber alertas quando meu nome aparecer</span>
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="profile-actions">
            <button type="submit" class="profile-save">Salvar perfil</button>
            <button type="button" class="profile-logout" data-auth-logout="true">Sair</button>
          </div>
        </form>

        <p class="profile-feedback" data-profile-feedback="true" hidden></p>
      </section>

      <section class="profile-empty" data-profile-empty="true">
        <span class="material-icons">manage_accounts</span>
        <h2>Entre para configurar seu perfil</h2>
        <p>Ao criar uma conta você poderá salvar preferências, treinar a experiência da busca e se preparar para funcionalidades premium no futuro.</p>
        <div class="profile-empty-actions">
          <button type="button" class="profile-save" data-auth-open="register">Criar conta</button>
          <button type="button" class="profile-ghost" data-auth-open="login">Já tenho conta</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>

  <%- include('./partials/auth-shell') %>
  <script src="/js/auth-ui.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/profile-ui.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
